  "title": "Senior/ Architect",
  "description": "<h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li>Take ownership of multiple project responsibilities within a collaborative project team environment.</li><li>Lead or contribute to large-scale projects in commercial, residential, healthcare, or infrastructure sectors.</li><li>Ensure coordination across disciplines and compliance with project timelines and design intent.</li><li>Exhibit strong creative thinking and design detailing skills.</li><li>Present a design portfolio that showcases a broad range of sustainable architecture and innovative solutions.</li><li>Proficiency in SketchUp, InDesign, and rendering/graphics software is preferred for conceptual and visual presentation work.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Demonstrated track record of project involvement and successful delivery.</li><li>Proficient in BIM/Revit, ArchiCAD, and AutoCAD.</li></ul><p>If interested, please submit your application to cvs@jdawms.com with your expected salary and resume.</p><p>We regret that only short-listed candidates will be contacted shortly. By submitting your application or resume, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and sharing of your personal information with potential employers for their assessment.</p><p>JDA WMS Pte Ltd | EA Personnel: Pham Thi Tuyet Mai</p><p>EA License No: 23S1595 | EA Registration No: R25127838</p>",
